text: Jahdet ar Oebbi leeqq ujahed iS. Neppa Ifren ikwen. Ur kwen Ihejjen ara di ddin, ddin ubabat wen Iboahim. Neppa, i wen isemman, zik, imvuaen. Deg waya, ad yili Umazan d anagi nnwen, u a ppilim d inagan n medden. Ihi, eeallet, zekkit, teiifem di Oebbi. Neppa d Bab nnwen. D Bab amxallef, d Asellak amxallef
